ZH: 我的姥姥今年已经六十岁了。
EN: My grandma is already sixty years old this year.

ZH: 我的姥姥很爱干净，家里总是打扫得一尘不染。
EN: My grandma is very clean, her house is always spotless.

ZH: 姥姥喜欢研究烹饪和烘培。
EN: Grandma likes to study cooking and baking.

ZH: 姥姥在我小时候给我讲了很多故事。
EN: My grandma told me a lot of stories when I was a kid.

ZH: 姥姥的手艺真的很好，每次做的菜都很好吃。
EN: Grandma's cooking skills are really great, her dishes taste delicious every time.

ZH: 我的姥姥很会缝纫，经常自己给我做衣服。
EN: My grandma is very good at sewing, she often makes clothes for me herself.

ZH: 姥姥最爱的孙子是我，她总是对我很宠爱。
EN: My grandma's favorite grandson is me, she always spoils me.

ZH: 姥姥是个很有耐心的人，不管我怎么调皮她都不生气。
EN: Grandma is a very patient person, no matter how mischievous I am, she never gets angry.

ZH: 我的姥姥身体一直很健康，几乎从不生病。
EN: My grandma has always been very healthy, she hardly ever gets sick.

ZH: 姥姥的脾气很好，从来不和别人争吵。
EN: Grandma has a good temper, she never argues with others.

ZH: 姥姥是个很善良的人，常常帮助邻居们。
EN: Grandma is a very kind person, she often helps her neighbors.

ZH: 姥姥很擅长织围巾和毛衣。
EN: Grandma is very good at knitting scarves and sweaters.

ZH: 姥姥曾经是个优秀的教师，教了几十年书。
EN: Grandma used to be an excellent teacher and taught for decades.

ZH: 姥姥有一只很可爱的猫咪，总是陪着她。
EN: Grandma has a very cute cat that always accompanies her.

ZH: 姥姥是个很传统的人，明年就要迎来她的八十大寿了。
EN: Grandma is a very traditional person, she will celebrate her 80th birthday next year.

ZH: 姥姥的书房里摆满了许多古董。
EN: Grandma's study is full of antiques.

ZH: 姥姥非常喜欢唱歌和跳舞。
EN: Grandma loves singing and dancing very much.

ZH: 姥姥是个很勤劳的人，总是早早起床做家务。
EN: Grandma is a very hardworking person, she always gets up early to do housework.

ZH: 姥姥是个很有智慧的人，总是给我很好的建议。
EN: Grandma is a very wise person, she always gives me good advice.

ZH: 我每周都会去姥姥家吃顿丰盛的晚饭。
EN: I go to grandma's house for a delicious dinner every week.
